19#include "ODRSSExpandedPair.h"
20
21#include <algorithm>
22#include <vector>
23
24namespace ZXing {
25namespace OneD {
26namespace RSS {
27
28/**
29* One row of an RSS Expanded Stacked symbol, consisting of 1+ expanded pairs.
30*/
31class ExpandedRow
32{
33 std::vector<ExpandedPair> _pairs;
34 int _rowNumber;
35 /** Did this row of the image have to be reversed (mirrored) to recognize the pairs? */
36 bool _wasReversed;
37
38public:
39 template <typename U>
40 ExpandedRow(const U& pairs, int rowNumber, bool wasReversed) : _rowNumber(rowNumber), _wasReversed(wasReversed) {
41 _pairs.reserve(pairs.size());
42 _pairs.assign(pairs.begin(), pairs.end());
43 }
44
45 const std::vector<ExpandedPair>& pairs() const {
46 return _pairs;
47 }
48
49 int rowNumber() const {
50 return _rowNumber;
51 }
52
53 bool wasReversed() const {
54 return _wasReversed;
55 }
56
57 template <typename U>
58 bool isEquivalent(const U& list) const {
59 return _pairs.size() == list.size() && std::equal(_pairs.begin(), _pairs.end(), list.begin());
60 }
61};
62
63} // RSS
64} // OneD
65} // ZXing
